The paper discusses the development of a web-based sizing tool prototype for SOA-based platforms, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed computing (cs.DC) concepts. The tool also aids in finding the optimum resources required to configure and implement a system, which involves data structures (cs.DS) and programming languages (cs.PL). Additionally, the tool predicts business growth, which involves system modeling and control (cs.SY).
